        "subject": "LU-1330 fid: prepare fid module for client server split",
        "message": "LU-1330 fid: prepare fid module for client server split\n\nMove the definition of struct seq_server_site to lustre_fid.h.  Remove\nobd_fid_{init,fini}() and replace with direct calls to\nclient_fid_{init,fini}().  Replace mdc_fid_alloc() with the new\nfunction client_fid_alloc().  Generally cleanup includes in\nlustre/fid/ and reduce the need for client code to directly or\nindirectly include {dt,md}_object.h.\n\nSigned-off-by: John L. Hammond <john.hammond@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Iea80f3d5d31705000510b5699bf32256bf003236\nSigned-off-by: John L. Hammond <john.hammond@intel.com>\n"
      },
